<h2><a name="seekdir" id="seekdir">seekdir</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

ios::seekdir
</p>

<p>
Possible values are:
</p>

<p>
ios::beg

</p>
<pre class="code">  The step size relative to the beginning of the stream. (Default).</pre>

<p>

ios::cur

</p>
<pre class="code">  The step size relative to the current position (as returned by tellp() of the stream).</pre>

<p>

ios::end

</p>
<pre class="code">  The step size relative to the end position of the the stream.</pre>

<p>

Related Topics: <a href="seekp" class="wikilink1" title="io:seekp">seekp</a>, <a href="seekg" class="wikilink1" title="io:seekg">seekg</a>

</p>

